Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Karen. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I've applied the discount to your cart. You should see the new total now.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I see it. Thanks.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, this is Larry. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, Larry. I need to cancel order H-998-776.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, thanks.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Mary. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, Mary. My order failed but I was charged. The order number is K-998-776.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry for the trouble. The charge you're seeing is a temporary hold that will be removed from your statement in a few days. The order did not go through.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, thank you for clarifying.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. You can try placing the order again.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I will. Thanks.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. Have a good day.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, this is Nate. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, Nate. I just want to know where my order is. The number is H-998-776.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check that for you. It looks like your order has shipped and is scheduled to be delivered tomorrow.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Great. Thanks for the update.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Olivia. How can I help you?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, Olivia. I received a damaged item. The order number is K-998-776.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry to hear that. I'm sending you a replacement right away. You can keep the damaged item as our apology.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I appreciate it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, this is Pete. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, Pete. I need to return an item. The order number is H-998-776.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can help with that. I'm sending you a pre-paid return label now.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Vince. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed an order, but I realized I used the wrong credit card. I need to change it. Order is P-5432.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me check the order status... I'm sorry, it has already been processed and the charge is complete. I can't change the payment method after the fact.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You can't do anything? Can you cancel it then?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Unfortunately, it's also too late to cancel as it's been sent to the warehouse. The only option would be to receive the order and then return it for a refund, and then you could re-purchase it with the correct card.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That is a huge, unnecessary hassle. Your system is not flexible at all.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I understand your frustration, and I'm very sorry for the inconvenience. That is the only process available once an order is locked for shipping.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Fine. Whatever. I'll just deal with it. So unhelpful.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I do apologize again.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, Wendy speaking.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I got a new TV from you, and it has a line of dead pixels running right down the middle of the screen.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh no, I'm so sorry to hear that. That's a clear manufacturing defect. We need to get that swapped out for you immediately. Can I have your order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: It's TV-1234.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I am setting up an exchange for you. We will have a new TV delivered to you. Because it's a large item, the delivery team that brings the new one will also pick up the defective one at the same time.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So they'll just swap them? That's great.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes. Our delivery partner will call you within 24 hours to schedule a convenient time for the swap. I am so sorry for the faulty product.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: It happens. Thanks for making the exchange so easy.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. We want you to have a perfect picture.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Xavier.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed order 123-KIDS-1 for a toy for my son's birthday. I just realized I ordered the wrong one. He wanted the blue robot, not the red one.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me see if I can fix that for you. Let me check the order... Yes, it's still processing. I can swap the red robot for the blue one for you. Would you like me to do that?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That would be a lifesaver! Yes, please.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, consider it done. I've updated the order to the blue robot. The price is the same. You'll get an updated confirmation email shortly.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You just saved my son's birthday. Thank you so much.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Happy to help save the day!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Yara. This call may be recorded.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I have a complaint about one of your in-store employees. I was just at your downtown location and the cashier was incredibly rude to me.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so sorry to hear that. That is not the experience we want for any of our customers. I can take your feedback and file a formal report with the store manager.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Please do. She was dismissive and sighed at me. Her name tag said 'Brenda'.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you for that information. I am creating a customer experience report right now with the store location, time, and employee name. This will be sent directly to the store manager and the district manager for review and follow-up.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Good. Her attitude was just awful.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so sorry you were treated that way. I've also added a $15 credit to your OmniMart account to apologize for the unpleasant visit. We appreciate you letting us know so we can address it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I appreciate you taking this seriously.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: We absolutely do.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Zane.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just saw on my credit card that my subscription for coffee renewed. I meant to cancel that last month. Can I get a refund?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can look into that for you. Let me pull up your account... I see the renewal charge from today. I can certainly cancel the subscription so it doesn't happen again.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: As for the refund, our policy is that we can refund renewal charges if you contact us before the item ships. Let me check the order status...

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Great news, it hasn't shipped yet. I can cancel this month's order and process a full refund for you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, that's perfect. Thank you so much.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, the subscription is cancelled, this month's order is cancelled, and the refund is processing. You'll get emails confirming all of that.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You've been a great help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with April.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi April, I need to cancel order 123-SALE-1. I bought a new coat, but I just saw that your competitor, 'The Coat Closet', has it for 30% less.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check on that for you. Let me see the order... I'm sorry, it has already been processed for shipping and I can't stop it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So I'm stuck paying more?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: 'The Coat Closet' is one of our approved competitors. Since it has already shipped, I can't cancel, but I can offer you a post-purchase price match. I can refund you the 30% difference right now.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You can do that? That would be fantastic! Yes, please.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Absolutely. I've just processed the refund. You'll get an email notification shortly. Your coat will arrive as planned, but at the lower price.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's amazing service. Thank you!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Brad.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just got an email saying my order is delayed by a week. I need those items for a trip this weekend. I have to cancel.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so sorry for that delay and the impact on your trip. Can I have the order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I see the delay notice from our warehouse. I apologize. Since the order has not shipped, I can cancel it for you immediately.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, please.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: The order has been cancelled, and you will receive a full refund. To apologize for our inventory/shipping issue, I've also added a $15 credit to your account.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, thank you. I appreciate that.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. I'm very sorry for the inconvenience and hope you have a wonderful trip.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Carol.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Carol, I just placed an order, number 123-FAIL-1. I got an error message on the site, but then I got a confirmation email. I just want to make sure it actually went through.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry for the confusing error message. I can definitely confirm the order status for you. Let me look it up...

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, I see order 123-FAIL-1 right here. It is confirmed and the payment was successful. It looks like it just showed you an error message by mistake.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, that's a relief. So I don't need to do anything?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Nope, your order is good to go. I will report the faulty error message to our technical team. Thank you for letting us know.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: No problem. Thanks for checking for me.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Dave.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed an order for a new blender. My husband just told me he bought one yesterday. I need to cancel my order, B-5432.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check on that for you. Let me see the status... Oh, I'm sorry, it has already been processed and is awaiting pickup by the courier. It's too late to stop it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Seriously? I placed it an hour ago.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Our warehouse is very efficient. I'm very sorry. Your best bet is to refuse the delivery when it arrives, and it will be returned to us for a full refund.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: What a hassle. Fine. I'll just refuse it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I've sent the return information to your email. I'm sorry for the inconvenience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Not your fault, I guess. Thanks.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Erica.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hello, I just placed an order, number 123-WRONG-1. I accidentally ordered 3 bags of dog food instead of 1. Can you change the quantity?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me see... Yes, the order is still processing. I can definitely adjust that for you. I've changed the quantity from 3 to 1.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I have also refunded the charge for the two extra bags back to your card. You'll get an updated confirmation email.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's perfect. Thank you for fixing my mistake so easily.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: My pleasure.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Frank.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just got an email with a 15% off coupon, but I made a big purchase yesterday. Can I apply the coupon to that order?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check on that for you. Generally, coupons cannot be applied retroactively to past orders. But since your order was so recent, let me see what I can do.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: As a one-time courtesy, I can honor that for you. I've just applied the 15% discount to yesterday's order and refunded the difference back to your payment method.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You can do that? That's amazing! Thank you so much.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: We appreciate your business. The refund confirmation email is on its way.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's great service.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Gloria.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Gloria, I'm trying to track my order, T-5432, and the courier website says 'delivery attempted, recipient not home'. But I was home all day, and no one ever knocked or rang the bell.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so sorry to hear that. That is very frustrating when drivers don't make a genuine attempt. Let me check the details...

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I see the same note. I am filing a complaint with the courier about a false delivery attempt. They will re-attempt delivery tomorrow. I've also requested that the driver be instructed to call you upon arrival. Can I confirm your number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, it's 555-123-4567. Thank you for doing that.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. And to apologize for the courier's failure and the delay, I have refunded your shipping fee.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you, I appreciate it. It was very annoying.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can only imagine. It will be there for you tomorrow.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Henry.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Henry, I received a new coffee maker today, and the glass carafe is broken. The box was pretty beat up.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm so sorry it arrived damaged. We can definitely get a replacement out to you. Do you need a whole new coffee maker, or just the glass carafe?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: The machine itself looks okay, so just the carafe would be fine.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Certainly. I've just placed an order for a replacement carafe to be sent to you, free of charge. There's no need to return the broken one, just please dispose of it carefully.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's great, thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. I'm also filing a damage claim with the courier for their rough handling. Your new carafe will ship today.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thanks for your help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Irene.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I'm calling to exchange a shirt for a different size. I've already sent the original back. The tracking shows you received it yesterday. When will my new size ship out?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check on that exchange for you. What was the order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I see the return was delivered yesterday. Our exchange process is that the new item ships once the return is inspected and processed by our team, which can take 3-5 business days after receipt.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So it hasn't shipped yet?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Not yet, but it is in the queue. It should be processed and shipped out within the next couple of days. You'll get a shipping confirmation email as soon as it's on its way.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, that's fine. I just wanted to make sure it was in the system.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: It is indeed. Thank you for your patience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Jack.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Jack, I'm trying to check out and my ShopSphere gift card is being declined.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry you're having trouble. Can you read me the gift card number so I can check its status?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: [customer reads number]

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. Let me check... I see the issue. The system shows that this gift card was already fully redeemed on an order two weeks ago. The current balance is zero.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: What? That's impossible, it's been in my wallet.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm very sorry. It's possible someone may have gotten the number and used it. I can see it was used on an order shipped to a different state. This sounds like fraud.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So my gift card was stolen? Can you do anything?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I need to transfer you to our Gift Card Fraud department. They can conduct a full investigation and see what can be done. Please hold.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: This is ridiculous. Okay, I'll hold.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Kim.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Kim, I need to sign out of my OmniMart account on a public computer I used, but I'm no longer there.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's a very smart security precaution. I can help you with that. Are you logged into your account on your phone or another device right now?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, on my phone.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Perfect. Go to 'My Account', then 'Login & Security'. In that section, you should see an option that says 'Sign out of all other devices'. If you click that and confirm, it will log you out everywhere except your current session.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I see it. 'Sign out of all other devices'. Okay, I've done it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Excellent. Your account is now secure and no longer logged in on that public computer.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's a fantastic feature. Thank you for your help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're very welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Leo.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I have a ShopSphere credit card and my rewards points balance seems wrong. It's much lower than it should be.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry to hear that. For specific issues with the credit card rewards program, I'll need to transfer you to our partners at the issuing bank. They manage the points calculations. Can you hold, please?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you for holding, you're with Card Services. My name is Megan. I can help with your points balance. Let me look up your account...I see the discrepancy. It looks like the '5x points on groceries' promotion from last quarter was not correctly applied to your account due to a system error. I am so sorry for that. I am manually calculating and adding the missing 2,500 points to your account right now. The corrected balance should be visible within the hour.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, thank you! I knew it was wrong.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: It was our error, and I apologize. The points are now corrected. Thank you for your patience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Maria.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Maria, I received a food processor from you today, and the main plastic bowl has a long crack down the side. It's unusable.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm so sorry it arrived damaged. That is definitely not the quality we aim for. I can help. Would you like a full replacement unit or just the bowl?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: The motor and blades seem fine, so just the bowl would be great.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Certainly. I am placing an order for a replacement bowl to be sent to you now, free of charge. No need to return the cracked one, just please recycle it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's perfect, thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: And for the trouble, I've also added a $10 credit to your account. I'm very sorry for the inconvenience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's very nice of you. Thanks for your help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. The new bowl will ship today.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Nate.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I want to return a camera, but it was part of a bundle that came with a free camera bag. Do I have to return the free bag too?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's a great question. Let me check the terms for that specific promotion. Can I get your order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I see the bundle here. The terms state that if you return the main item (the camera), you must also return the promotional item (the camera bag) to receive a full refund. If you keep the bag, its value of $29.99 will be deducted from your refund.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, that makes sense. I'll return both then.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Perfect. I'm sending you the return label now, which will cover both items. Just be sure to pack them both in the same box.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Will do. Thanks for explaining the policy.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.text: It seems the code is only valid for first-time customers. I can offer you a 10% discount on your order today.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That would be great. Thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I've applied the discount to your cart. You should see the new total now.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I see it. Thanks.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, this is Nate. How can I help?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, Nate. I need to cancel order H-998-776.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: It looks like your order has shipped. You can refuse the delivery or return it for a refund.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, thanks.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Irene. How can I assist?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed an order, but I need to cancel it. My daughter just told me she already bought the same item as a gift for me. Order is G-5432.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's a thoughtful daughter! Let me check if I can cancel that for you... Yes, the order is still processing. I can cancel it right now.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, wonderful. Thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: It's all cancelled. You'll receive a confirmation email shortly, and you haven't been charged. Enjoy your gift!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you for the quick help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, Jack speaking.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Jack, my order was supposed to be delivered by your in-house delivery service, but the driver just marked it as 'undeliverable' and the tracking shows it's being returned. Why?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm so sorry for that. That shouldn't have happened. Let me look up the order and the driver's notes. Can I have the order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you... I see the note. The driver has marked it as 'No Secure Location'. Do you live in an apartment building?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, but there's a locked lobby. He just needed to buzz my apartment.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I see. It sounds like the driver did not make a proper attempt. I am so sorry. Since the package is already on its way back, the best I can do is place a new order for you, with express shipping, at no charge.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: This is a huge inconvenience. I'm cancelling. Just give me a refund.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. A full refund will be processed as soon as the package arrives back. I've also added a $20 credit to your account to apologize for our driver's failure.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Fine. This whole experience was terrible.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I understand and I'm very sorry.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Kim.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just tried to place an order, but my card was declined. I know the card is good. What's the problem?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry you're having trouble. Let me check the failed transaction... The reason we received from the bank is 'Incorrect CVC'. It seems the 3-digit security code on the back of the card was entered incorrectly.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, I must have fat-fingered it. So the order didn't go through?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's correct. No order was placed and you were not charged. You can simply try placing the order again and enter the code carefully.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, I'll do that. Thanks for your help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Leo. This call may be recorded.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hello, I bought a new video game, but I just saw it's on the 'GameSphere' digital store for $20 less. I want to cancel. Order is G-1234.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I understand. Let me check your order status... I'm sorry, it has already been packaged and has a shipping label. It's too late to cancel.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So I can't cancel and you don't price match digital stores, right?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's correct. We can't match digital download prices for physical games. Your only option would be to return the game for a refund once it arrives.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: But if I open it to play it, I can't return it?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Also correct. Opened software is not eligible for return.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: This is a terrible situation. So I either wait, don't play it, return it, and then buy it from the other store, or I just pay more. Your policies are not customer-friendly.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I understand your frustration, and I've noted your feedback on our policies. I've sent the return label to your email, should you choose that path.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Fine. Thanks for nothing.

Sub_Intent: Found a Better Price or Offer Elsewhere

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, Maria speaking.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed an order, O-1234, and I realized I had it shipped to my old address. I moved last year.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me see if I can catch that for you... I'm very sorry, but our system has already processed the order and generated the shipping label. I cannot change the address or cancel it at this point.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You can't do anything? It's going to an empty house!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am very sorry for this situation. Since the address is incorrect, the courier will likely be unable to deliver it and will return it to us. Once it's returned, you will be automatically refunded.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So I just have to wait for it to hopefully get sent back? This is because I forgot to delete one address from my profile. Your system should make you confirm the address!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That is excellent feedback, and I will pass it on. I understand this is frustrating. I've placed a note on the order to expedite the refund as soon as it's returned. I am very sorry for the inconvenience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Fine. There's nothing else to do, I guess.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Nate.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I have a complaint. I ordered a new office chair and paid for the 'Expert Assembly' service. The delivery team just dropped the box in my living room and left.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so sorry to hear that. They absolutely did not complete the service you paid for. I can fix this. Can I have your order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I see the charge for the assembly service. I am refunding that for you right now, in full. But I also want to get your chair assembled. I can schedule a dedicated assembly technician to come to your home tomorrow to build it for you. Would that work?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So I get the fee back AND someone will still come build it?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes. The assembly will be free of charge, to make up for the delivery team's failure. I am so sorry for this experience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, that's a great way to handle it. Yes, please schedule the technician.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I have scheduled it. They will call you to confirm a time. The refund is processing. My apologies again.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, Olivia speaking.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I'd like to exchange a dress for a smaller size, but I'm going out of town tomorrow for a week. Can I send my return back when I get home?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. Our return policy gives you 30 days from the date you receive the item, so you have plenty of time. Would you like me to email you the return label now so you have it ready?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, please. The order is D-5432.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, I've sent the label. And would you like me to set up the exchange for the smaller size now?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, please.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I've set up the exchange. The new size will ship out to you as soon as the original one is scanned as returned by the post office. So it won't ship while you're away.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's perfect. It will all be taken care of when I get back. Thank you!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. Enjoy your trip.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, this is Peter.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I have a question about my account. I was trying to add my work address for a delivery, but it says I can't add any more addresses.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can clarify that. Our system limits the number of saved addresses in an account's address book to ten, for security reasons.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, I have sent gifts to a lot of people. I guess I'm at ten.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's a common issue for our generous customers! To add a new address, you would first need to go into your address book and delete an old one that you no longer need.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I see. Okay, I can do that. I'll delete my old cousin's address.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Once you've done that, the 'Add New Address' button should work for you again.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Perfect. Thanks for the explanation.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, Rachel speaking.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I'm calling about a charge on my credit card. I don't recognize it. It's for $89.99.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can look into that for you. Do you have an order number, or can I get your name?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: The name is John Smith.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you, John. Let me check your order history... I see an order from two days ago for a new video game, 'Dragon's Lair 4', for that amount. The shipping address is 123 Main Street.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh my goodness. My son. He must have used my card which is saved on his console. I'm so sorry.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: It happens! Would you like me to see if I can cancel the order for you?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, please, if you can.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me check the status... I'm so sorry, but it has already shipped and is on its way.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Drat. Okay, well, I guess we'll be having a conversation about it when it arrives, and he'll be returning it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I've sent the return label to your email to help with that. I'd also suggest removing your saved payment info from his console to prevent future surprises!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Way ahead of you. Thanks for your help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, this is Sam.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Sam, I just used your 'WELCOME20' coupon for 20% off my first order, but it seems like it didn't take 20% off the total.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Welcome to OmniMart! Let me clarify how that coupon works. The 20% discount is applied to the subtotal of eligible items, before tax and shipping fees are calculated.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, so it doesn't apply to tax and shipping?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: That's correct. Our coupons don't reduce government-mandated taxes or our standard shipping charges. So the final total won't be exactly 20% less than the grand total.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, that makes sense now. The math just seemed off. Thank you for explaining.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're very welcome. We're happy to have you as a new customer.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Tess.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed order C-1234. I'm having second thoughts about the color. Can I cancel it?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me check the status for you... Yes, it's still in our processing system. I can cancel it for you. Are you sure? I could also just change the color for you if you'd like.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You know what, I think I need to see them in person. Let's just cancel for now.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Not a problem. I have cancelled the order. You'll receive a confirmation email shortly, and you have not been charged.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you for being so flexible.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. We're here when you decide!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Uma.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, my order is supposed to be delivered today, but I have a last-minute appointment. Is there any way to know what time it will arrive?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check that for you. What is your tracking number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I'm looking at the detailed courier information... Unfortunately, they only provide a general delivery window of 8 AM to 8 PM. They don't give a more specific time.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So I have no way of knowing?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: What I can do for you is add 'Delivery Instructions' to your tracking, asking the driver to leave the package at your back door. Would that work for you?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, that would be perfect. Please add that note.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I have just updated the instructions. The driver will now see a note requesting they leave it at the back door. Hopefully that helps!

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: It does. Thank you so much for your help.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Vince.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I ordered a new rug, but it's much darker in person than it looked on your website. I need to return it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry to hear the color wasn't a good match. That can be tricky online. I can definitely help you with the return. Can I get your order number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. For a large item like a rug, we do have to arrange a freight pickup. Do you still have the original plastic wrapping it came in?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, I kept everything.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Perfect. I have initiated the return and scheduled the pickup. Our freight partner will call you in the next day to arrange a convenient time. Once we receive it back, you'll get a full refund.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, that sounds straightforward. Thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. Sorry again about the color.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Wendy.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hello, I just received my order for a new pair of earrings, but the box is empty. The earrings are gone.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh no, that's terrible! I am so sorry. It sounds like the package may have been tampered with in transit. Let me look up your order.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: The order is E-1234.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I am so sorry this happened. I am shipping you a new pair of earrings right now, with our fastest shipping. I am also filing a theft investigation with the courier service.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, thank you. I was so upset when I opened the box.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can only imagine. To apologize for this major failure, I have also refunded your original purchase in full. The replacement pair is a gift from us.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: You're refunding me and sending a new pair? Wow. Thank you so much.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: It is the least we can do. I am so sorry for this experience.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Xavier.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just got an email that my order, O-5432, was cancelled due to a payment issue. But I checked with my bank and there's nothing wrong with my card.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm sorry for that cancellation. Let me check the transaction details... I see. The order was cancelled by our automated fraud system. This is usually triggered by a mismatch in information.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I see that the shipping address you entered is different from the card's billing address, and it's a high-value item. The system flagged it as potentially fraudulent for your protection.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: But it was me! I was sending a gift to my son.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I understand, and I do apologize. The system can be overly cautious. Once it's cancelled, I cannot reinstate it. The best thing to do is place the order again, and perhaps call your bank beforehand to let them know you're making a purchase that will be shipped to a different address.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: What a hassle. Okay, I'll try that. Thanks for explaining.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. Sorry for the extra steps.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Yara.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Yara, I placed an order, O-1234, and paid extra for Saturday delivery. It's Saturday, and the tracking says it's now scheduled for Monday. This is not what I paid for.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so sorry for that failed delivery promise. You are absolutely right to be upset. Let me look at that order...

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I see the courier has had a local delay and missed the Saturday window. I sincerely apologize. I have already refunded your Saturday delivery fee in full.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I appreciate that, but I needed the item for an event today.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I understand completely. Since it will no longer be useful to you when it arrives on Monday, I have also sent you a free return label. You can refuse the delivery or send it back for a full refund.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay. I'll do that. I'm very disappointed in the service.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I know. And for failing you so badly on this, I've also added a $25 credit to your account. I am so sorry for the impact this had on your plans.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay. Thank you for that. I appreciate you trying to make it right.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Zane.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I just placed an order for a new dress, D-1234, but I was just looking at your competitor 'Fashion Forward' and they have a very similar dress for $40 less.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I can check on that for you. Is it the exact same dress from the same brand?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: No, it's their own store brand, but it's almost identical.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Ah, I see. Unfortunately, our price match policy only applies to identical items, meaning the same brand and model number. We can't match prices on similar-looking items from a competitor's store brand.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh. Well, in that case, I'd like to cancel my order.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Let me check the status... The order is still processing. I can go ahead and cancel that for you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Yes, please.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Okay, the order has been cancelled. You'll receive a confirmation email shortly.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you for your help.

Sub_Intent: Found a Better Price or Offer Elsewhere

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with April.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi, I placed an order for two lamps, but I just noticed I was only charged for one. The packing slip shows two. What should I do?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you so much for your honesty in calling us about that! Let me look up your order. Can I have the number?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you. I see the order. You are absolutely right, it looks like there was a billing error and we only charged you for one of the lamps. Thank you again for reporting it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: So, how do I pay for the other one?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You know what, because you were so honest and took the time to call us, we'd like you to keep the second lamp on us. Please consider it a gift as a thank you for being a great customer.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Really? I can just keep it? I was fully prepared to pay for it.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: We appreciate that, but please, enjoy it. It was our error, but your honesty is what matters.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Wow. Thank you so much. That's incredible.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Brad.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Brad, I just placed an order, number 123-WRONG-1, but I just realized I ordered 10 boxes of pens instead of 1. It was a typo.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh my, that's a lot of pens! Let me see if I can fix that for you. Let me check the order... Yes, it's still processing. I can adjust the quantity for you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you! I definitely don't need 10 boxes.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I have changed the quantity from 10 to 1. I've also refunded the difference back to your credit card. You'll get an updated confirmation email showing the correct quantity and price.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: That's a huge relief. Thank you for fixing my mistake.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're very welcome.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: OmniMart, you're with Carol.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hi Carol, I got a new food scale from you and it's not working correctly. It keeps giving me different weights for the same item. It's not accurate.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I'm very sorry to hear that the scale is defective. That defeats its entire purpose. I can help you with that. Would you like a replacement or a full refund?

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: I'd like to try a replacement. Maybe I just got a bad one.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: Of course. I am sending you a new scale right now. There's no need to return the defective one, please just recycle it as e-waste.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Oh, that's easy. Thank you.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: And to apologize for the faulty product, I've added a $10 credit to your account as well.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Thank you, that's very nice.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: You're welcome. Your new scale will be with you shortly.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: ShopSphere, this is Dave.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: customer
Transcript_Segments.text: Hello, I just received my order of a new watch, and the box is empty. The watch is missing, and the box looks like it was opened and re-taped.

Transcript_Segments.speaker: agent
Transcript_Segments.text: I am so incredibly sorry to hear that. It sounds like your package was stolen from or tampered with in transit. This is a very serious issue.
